title: 2 Bedroom, Close to Shopping, Freeways, Public Transportation & More!
posting_body: ['Experience Comfort and Convenience.', 'Alvista Lake Meridian offers four floor plans to choose from.', 'Our spacious one, two, and three bedroom options include 9-foot ceilings, an all-electric kitchen, a breakfast bar, ceiling fans, and an in-home washer and dryer.', 'Cozy up to your wood burning fireplace or watch the sunsets from your own balcony or patio.', 'We are a pet-friendly community and offer plenty of walking space.', 'You are sure to find what you are looking for here at Alvista Lake Meridian Apartments.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 83', 'OR Text', '83', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact us.', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 900 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Balcony or Patio', '- Refrigerator', '- Laundry Room*', '- Carpeted Floors', '- Disability Access', '- Wood Burning Fireplace', '- 9Ft Ceilings', '- Extra Storage', '- Dishwasher', '- Washer and Dryer in Home', '- Views Available', '- All-electric Kitchen', '- Vaulted Ceilings*', '- Cable Ready', '- Vertical Blinds', '- Ceiling Fans', '*In Select Apartment Homes', 'Community Amenities', '- Short-term Leasing Available', '- Shimmering Swimming Pool', "- Children's Play Area", '- Section 8 Welcome', '- State-of-the-art Fitness Center', '- Easy Access to Freeways and Shopping', '- Soothing Hot Tub', '- Covered Parking', '- Public Parks Nearby', '- Guest Parking', '- Beautiful Landscaping', '- Access to Public Transportation', '- Cable Available', '- On-call Maintenance', '- Assigned Parking', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Friendly.', 'Restricted Breeds.', '$250 pet deposit/$250 pet fee.', '$50 pet rent.', '2 max pets.', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5 time gross monthly income', 'Office Hours', 'Tuesday-Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Alvista Lake Meridian', '14901 SE 272nd St, Kent, WA, 98042', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', '8onI3NyK7YUL']
